tron = Movie('Tron Legacy 2010')
functions = [tron.add_to_library, tron.add_to_collection, tron.
    add_to_watchlist, tron.dismiss, tron.mark_as_unseen, tron.
    remove_from_library, tron.remove_from_collection, tron.
    remove_from_watchlist, tron.mark_as_seen]
for fn in functions:
    r = fn()
    assert r is None
